revisions.description: Fixed parse errors and warnings and incorrect string sizes. Added object to control if an interface should use its VLAN settings. Added the ability to modify several objects regarding interfaces, HMS, time, NTP, SNMP and module redundancy settings. Added object to enable/disable user authentication for modules and to create and upload/download individual settings backups for modules. Added value to update a module's entitlements. Updated contact information.
